{"tid":2325923,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法國足球公布歷史最佳陣容，梅西、C羅、比利和馬拉度納等人入選","createTime":"2020-12-15T02:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T12:15:19.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"784fe3b58e5f53b383fed84281abdde9bbe54809","tid":2325923,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T02:49:18.000Z","msg":"《法國足球》評選的歷史最佳11人昨日公布，第一隊梅西、C羅、比利和馬拉度納等人入選，近代傳奇中場皮爾洛和席丹則入選了第二隊。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F8fdz2PDg9RekYnLsgYv.A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/__80/481f9bfa57241113e891387d8f403659\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FF8fdz2PDg9RekYnLsgYv.A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2F__80%2F481f9bfa57241113e891387d8f403659&h=fcf06deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（歷史最佳陣容。圖片來源：Twitter）<br />\n<br />\n本屆的金球獎由於新冠病毒的原因而取消了，《法國足球》改為評選歷史「最佳11人」，排位分為門將、左後衛、右後衛、中後衛、防守中場、進攻中場、左邊鋒、右邊鋒和中鋒九個位置，歷史最佳陣容由全球170位記者投票。最終，梅西、C羅、大羅、比利和馬拉度納等人入選了第一陣容。皮爾洛、席丹、小羅和巴雷西等傳奇則被排入第二隊。<br />\n<br />\n最佳11人第一隊：<br />\n<br />\n門將：雅辛<br />\n<br />\n後衛：貝肯鮑爾、馬爾蒂尼、卡福<br />\n<br />\n中場：哈維、馬特烏斯、比利、馬拉多納<br />\n<br />\n前鋒：C羅、大羅、梅西<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/96n1a8MfnfsJNE0JUU67bA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/__80/54cbc55320f600afef05ccc4d64a05bf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F96n1a8MfnfsJNE0JUU67bA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2F__80%2F54cbc55320f600afef05ccc4d64a05bf&h=8d61aad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（歷史最佳陣容。圖片來源：Twitter）<br />\n<br />\n最佳11人第二隊：<br />\n<br />\n門將：布馮<br />\n<br />\n後衛：卡洛斯、巴雷西、阿爾貝托<br />\n<br />\n中場：迪斯蒂法諾、里杰卡爾德、皮爾洛、席丹<br />\n<br />\n前鋒：小羅、克魯伊夫、加林查<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tPC3AnbC3G4GJJ9wftbGNA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/__80/29c9ab44eb0fcc9376bad07c1f85f9f6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtPC3AnbC3G4GJJ9wftbGNA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2F__80%2F29c9ab44eb0fcc9376bad07c1f85f9f6&h=77d2fbca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（歷史最佳陣容第二隊。圖片來源：Twitter）<br />\n<br />\n最佳11人第三陣容：<br />\n<br />\n門將：諾伊爾<br />\n<br />\n後衛：布萊特納、拉莫斯、拉姆<br />\n<br />\n中場：伊涅斯塔、迪迪、內斯肯斯、普拉蒂尼<br />\n<br />\n前鋒：亨利、范巴斯滕、貝斯特<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nEiTklLB2xP58j1A0ZgNeA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/__80/85affa5e26d2e7ea6060d2d68a5022fd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnEiTklLB2xP58j1A0ZgNeA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2F__80%2F85affa5e26d2e7ea6060d2d68a5022fd&h=f0f9b109&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d54367a409c8da243e03f1f204667b052b8544f7","tid":2325923,"uid":234945,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:00:24.000Z","msg":"頂你個肺咩，譯名都唔hi轉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1f50675b76f4f270a6e48607391a754fe99212","tid":2325923,"uid":166733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:19:34.000Z","msg":"Xavi第一隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764518bbff27755426bd801121d100c3572db434","tid":2325923,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:29:41.000Z","msg":"霉閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811b1e9c71ae74bea2798892b8e5b6e990d782b4","tid":2325923,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T07:41:04.000Z","msg":"識野喎  識用馬特烏斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"